# solution.py
from typing import List, Optional, Dict, Set, Any

class Solution:
    def findSecret(self, text: str) -> str:
        """
        Extracts the last word from the provided text, which is guaranteed to be the secret word.
        
        :param text: The input text containing the secret word at the very end.
        :return: The secret word found in the text.
        """
        # Split the text into words
        words = text.split()
        # Return the last word
        return words[-1]
